# Python script for download animes from Nyaa.si RSS using filters for select which episode will be downloaded

# Implemented:
    * JSON (For read and write config)
    * BeautifulSoup and lxml: To get info from RSS
    * Paho-MQTT: To get and send info using MQTT protocol
    * libtorrent: To connect a torrent aggregator and download anime files.
    * Requests: Get RSS file from WEB
    * Threading: Just for isolate MQTT code

